# Godot
# .godot/ is the per-machine import cache and must be ignored. The
# per-asset .import sidecar files (e.g. NotoColorEmoji.ttf.import)
# carry import-time params (disable_embedded_bitmaps, fallbacks, …)
# that need to round-trip through git, so they are NOT ignored here
# despite older Godot project templates suggesting otherwise.
client/.godot/
client/.import/
client/build/
client/export.cfg
client/export_credentials.cfg
*.translation

# Smoke-test screenshots dumped at the repo root by playwright drives
/*.png
